                                        <li class="mb-2"><i class="ti ti-check text-orange me-2"></i>8-minute games</li>
                                        <li class="mb-2"><i class="ti ti-check text-orange me-2"></i>2-minute breaks</li>
                                        <li class="mb-2"><i class="ti ti-check text-orange me-2"></i>Running clock until final minute</li>
                                        <li class="mb-2"><i class="ti ti-check text-orange me-2"></i>Stop clock in final minute</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-md-6">
                                    <h5 class="text-orange mb-3">Shot Clock</h5>
                                    <ul class="list-unstyled">
                                        <li class="mb-2"><i class="ti ti-check text-orange me-2"></i>Standard for first 7 minutes</li>
                                        <li class="mb-2"><i class="ti ti-check text-orange me-2"></i>Half game clock (>10 sec remaining)</li>
                                        <li class="mb-2"><i class="ti ti-check text-orange me-2"></i>Full game clock (≤10 sec remaining)</li>
                                        <li class="mb-2"><i class="ti ti-check text-orange me-2"></i>Fair player rotation system</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

